#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cvendor-integration.md:7
msgid ""
"The Vendor tab is used when a commercial vendor has built an implementation "
"of your service's reference decision model. It lets you record that vendor's "
"details, link their implementation to your reference service, and track "
"certification status — all as queryable Linked Data."
msgstr ""

