msgid ""
"Open the vendor dropdown. Vendors are loaded from the RONL vocabulary in "
"TriplyDB — this may take a moment."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cvendor-integration.md:15
msgid ""
"Select the vendor. The form below the dropdown updates to show the fields "
"for that vendor's integration."
